snippet.title: Diana and Roma Family summer vacation
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma are actively and cheerfully spending time outdoors, swimming and sunbathing, strengthening their health during the summer holidays. Our family had a great time at Nirvana Mediterranean Excellence in Turkey.
Thanks for watching!
